<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="64" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,965,1477]" pageId="1" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,318,1170,1196]" pageId="1" pageNumber="64">Diagnosis</emphasis>
Shell large, 119.8–148.0 mm in height, sculptured with various sized spiral cords, peripheral keel not prominent. Sinus deep, narrow, on a spiral rib immediately above the peripheral carina.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,965,1477]" box="[198,862,1250,1277]" pageId="1" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,294,1250,1276]" pageId="1" pageNumber="64">Habitat</emphasis>
